<concept id="concept_FAFDCB5BC3864E738EE94DFD0478CF59" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>About this Manual</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>This manual describes the tasks of technology providers in order to prepare software applications for usage in a SaaS model and integrate them with <ph
                    product="oscm_ce"><ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Name"/> (<ph
                        conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/></ph>) <ph
                    product="oscm_ee">FUJITSU Software Enterprise Service Catalog Manager, hereafter referred to as <ph
                        conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/></ph>.</p>
            <p>The manual is structured as follows: </p>
            <p>
                <table colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
                    <tgroup cols="2">
                        <colspec colname="col2" colnum="1" colwidth="1.0*"/>
                        <colspec colname="col3" colnum="2" colwidth="1.31*"/>
                        <thead>
                            <row>
                                <entry colname="col2">Chapter</entry>
                                <entry colname="col3">Description</entry>
                            </row>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry colname="col2"><xref href="../../Shared/concepts/c_IntroExtended.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry colname="col3"
                                    >Explains how to prepare applications for SaaS and gives an overview of the integration tasks. </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry><xref href="../AccessTypes/c_AccessTypes.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry colname="col3"
                                        >Describes how users can access an application that is integrated with <ph
                                        conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>. </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry colname="col2"><xref href="../Implement/c_Implement.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry>Describes how to implement the interfaces between an application and <ph
                                        conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>.</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry colname="col2"><xref href="../Provision/c_Provision.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry colname="col3">Describes how to register applications as services in <ph
                                        conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                    /> and appoint suppliers for them. </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry colname="col2"><xref href="../Reports/c_Reports.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry>Describes the reports available for technology providers in <ph
                                        conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>. </entry>
                            </row>
                            <!--row>
                                <entry colname="col2"><xref href="../Reference/r_MenuOptions.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry colname="col3"
                                    >Gives an overview of the menu options relevant for technology providers.</entry>
                            </row-->
                            <row>
                                <entry colname="col2"><xref href="../Reference/r_TechServDescr.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry colname="col3">Describes the elements of a technical service definition.</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry colname="col2"><xref href="../Reference/c_APP.xml"/></entry>
                                <entry colname="col3">Describes the Asynchronous Provisioning Platform (APP).</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                    </tgroup>
                </table>
            </p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
